{"tid":1467553,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"813機場一役想反敗為勝嘅同我全部入哂嚟！","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:23:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:35:05.000Z","uid":31744,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"11040f5c35c036ac7b69b6c5e38f00209f5251fe","tid":1467553,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:23:07.000Z","msg":"1. 和理非聽日全部入哂機場搞道歉大會，勇武休息一日<br />\n<br />\n2. 盡量協助外國旅客順利登機（中國旅客自行決定）<br />\n<br />\n3. 態度一定要誠懇有禮貌（直情成個空姐咁就得）<br />\n<br />\n4. 制止所有搞事、煽動群眾嘅暴力行為"},{"pid":"4ca94a02871a40d7563ccfde9c5332d345f32937","tid":1467553,"uid":41010,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:24:06.000Z","msg":"第一，請停止在機場勇武，機場係和理非嘅地方，有時間係機場勇武不如做多啲文宣<br />\n<br />\n第二，唔好再捉鬼，唔會捉得晒，喺機場你去做文宣唔駛塞晒條路留返一小部分俾人行就自然會塞，所以啲鬼做乜都冇用，唔該記得你個目的係癱瘓機場<br />\n<br />\n第三，唔好玩膠，今日捉到公安又話遊街又話錫春袋，如果你去機場係認為可以玩玩吓，唔該自己返屋企攝高個枕頭諗清楚"},{"pid":"e01bd974f818a45b5b6d9299d7f2505bde541f66","tid":1467553,"uid":25866,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:24:27.000Z","msg":"請大家入機場前備戰、坐公共交通前就要上裝<br />\n防cctv 因為會有機會好似今日咁打狗救手足<br />\n口罩、帽，仲有耳仔<br />\n全黑衣服、飲水、食野請小心"},{"pid":"53a3f27cf9e7ec1e04c2ba7a02c0e1ed0d53373e","tid":1467553,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:24:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有<br />\n唔會捉得晒<br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e1f20a4809f5a7d9281dde2da0d8e60cabdfde","tid":1467553,"uid":13732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:24:53.000Z","msg":"機場捉公安見聞及想問大家一個問題<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467325\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467325</a>"},{"pid":"f9239a2500b568f75dc3e30f4c5e2719fc09a848","tid":1467553,"uid":25866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:25:08.000Z","msg":"請大家入機場前備戰、坐公共交通前就要上裝<br />\n防cctv 因為會有機會好似今日咁打狗救手足<br />\n口罩、帽，仲有耳仔<br />\n全黑衣服、飲水、食野請小心"},{"pid":"4c4d16c4003fd7d760d806ba19165fc3f0c5033f","tid":1467553,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:27:34.000Z","msg":"［正視聽］大家唔好再嘈啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464495\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464495</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8a5c7041138082075ea42dbba38a836c2fa8878b","tid":1467553,"uid":80234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:27:58.000Z","msg":"贊成道歉<br />\n<br />\n[推俾民間記者會戰友睇］［Damage Control] 機場圍公安事件應對公關<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466185\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466185</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"aa66757021f5205d87da3e7532c5c9ca9904f6aa","tid":1467553,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:30:41.000Z","msg":"先要塞機場嘅手足肯聽意見<br />\n願意group thinking<br />\n佢地又選擇塞離境就其他人做咩都冇用"},{"pid":"637fc9d9dff85da2c6c1ea516b0d75f698b9dfb9","tid":1467553,"uid":260088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:35:05.000Z","msg":"［置頂］［緊急］ 民間記者會請幫手